headline: What Analyst Projections for Key Metrics Reveal About Dominion Energy (D) Q4 Earnings
summary: Beyond analysts' top-and-bottom-line estimates for Dominion Energy (D), evaluate projections for some of its key metrics to gain a better insight into how the business might have performed for the quarter ended December 2025.
